# Convert Python Notebooks to Python Scripts

## Installing requirements and converting notebooks to scripts

1. Install ipython libraries and nbconvert

    `pip3 install ipython nbconvert`

1. Run the following command to convert the python notebooks into python Scripts 

    It can also be converted to all these formats: ['asciidoc', 'custom', 'html', 
    'latex', 'markdown', 'notebook', 'pdf', 'python', 'rst', 'script', 'slides', 
    'webpdf']

    `jupyter nbconvert *.ipynb --to python`

    NOTE: `ipython nbconvert` has been deprecated

